  "title": "Resident Care Officer - North East | 5 Days - Up to $3.3k [0580]",
  "description": "<ul><li>Salary : $2,500 - $3,300</li><li>Location: Buangkok</li><li>Working hours: 5 days - 44 hours / week </li><li>Rotating shift : 8:30am - 6:30pm / 8am - 8pm (AM) / 8pm - 8am  (PM)</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and supervise the care of residents</li><li>Develop and implement programmes and activities for the well-being of residents</li><li>Put up monthly interview records for residents</li><li>Ensure proper maintenance of the Home's equipment</li><li>Ensure the cleanliness of the Home premises</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in psychology , social work , counselling or relevant field</li><li>Willing to work rotating shifts including night shift and weekends</li><li>Training provided</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
